    It is <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_source">Open-Source</a> software which means that end users and developers have freedom to study, to improve and to redistribute the program (<a href="{{ path('bwf_license') }}">Public domain</a> for the code developed by us).<br/>
</section>
{% endblock %}
